Class Real

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cafean.Number.BaseNumber
      • com.cafean.Number.Real
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.awt.datatransfer.Transferable, java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Comparable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Angle, Density, Dimless, Enthalpy, Pressure, RealBean, SpecEnergy, Temperature, Time
    public class Real
extends BaseNumber
implements java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Comparable, java.awt.datatransfer.Transferable
    Real is base class for all ModelEditor floating point numbers.
